      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental samples used for validation must be fully characterized for biological variability, hematocrit, and storage conditions; sample size must be statistically justified.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization not assessed at the required level. Biological variability across blood samples not reported and sample size justification absent. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
